 yeah, there was a lot of Holy Spirit there.

797
00:47:35,960 --> 00:47:38,060
 You need to be filled with the Holy Spirit.

798
00:47:38,060 --> 00:47:40,440
 And actually to be filled with the Holy Spirit,

799
00:47:40,440 --> 00:47:42,240
 you need to be emptied of yourself.

800
00:47:42,240 --> 00:47:45,300
 Many of us do.

801
00:47:45,300 --> 00:47:46,940
 We're too full of ourselves.

802
00:47:50,060 --> 00:47:52,820
 So just take this time as you put your hands out

803
00:47:52,820 --> 00:47:56,880
 to empty yourself.

804
00:47:56,880 --> 00:48:06,140
 And Father, we ask that you would come to your church,

805
00:48:06,140 --> 00:48:10,820
 here in this building, online, wherever people are listening,

806
00:48:10,820 --> 00:48:14,400
 and fill us once again with your Holy Spirit.

807
00:48:14,400 --> 00:48:18,000
 We need you.

808
00:48:18,000 --> 00:48:19,440
 We need you desperately.

809
00:48:19,440 --> 00:48:22,020
 (gentle music)

810
00:48:22,020 --> 00:48:30,000
 Do you realize 94% of people in Hong Kong are not Christian?

811
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:37,680
 They need you to be filled with the Holy Spirit today,

812
00:48:37,680 --> 00:48:41,040
 so the 6% can reach the 94%.

813
00:48:41,040 --> 00:48:43,620
 (gentle music)

814
00:48:43,620 --> 00:48:48,200
 Do you recognize the worldview around the world

815
00:48:48,200 --> 00:48:52,320
 is going decidedly non-Christian?

816
00:48:52,320 --> 00:49:00,440
 They need Christians who will be full of the Holy Spirit,

817
00:49:00,440 --> 00:49:02,240
 who will speak up for the gospel.

818
00:49:02,240 --> 00:49:09,760
 You might be saying, "Hey, look, it's not me."

819
00:49:09,760 --> 00:49:13,080
 You know, I understand, John,

820
00:49:13,080 --> 00:49:14,760
 how you'd talk to the taxi driver

821
00:49:14,760 --> 00:49:17,160
 and the guy on the bus, you'd talk to anybody,

822
00:49:17,160 --> 00:49:18,500
 but that's just not me.

823
00:49:18,500 --> 00:49:21,120
 Guys, it's not an option.

824
00:49:21,120 --> 00:49:23,060
 It is you.

825
00:49:23,060 --> 00:49:27,280
 There are people in your workplace.

826
00:49:27,280 --> 00:49:28,880
 There are people in your family.

827
00:49:28,880 --> 00:49:32,760
 There are people in your circle

828
00:49:32,760 --> 00:49:36,940
 that God has ordained you to speak to.

829
00:49:36,940 --> 00:49:43,360
 It might start off by you just doing

830
00:49:43,360 --> 00:49:45,380
 a random act of kindness for them.

831
00:49:45,980 --> 00:49:48,560
 (gentle music)

832
00:49:48,560 --> 00:49:52,300
 And being able to follow up that,

833
00:49:52,300 --> 00:49:55,020
 "Yes, I was able to do this because I'm a Christian."

834
00:49:55,020 --> 00:49:59,400
 Can I pray for you?

835
00:49:59,400 --> 00:50:07,820
 Do you know, I've lived in Hong Kong 35 years,

836
00:50:07,820 --> 00:50:12,820
 and I've asked the question, "Can I pray for you?"

837
00:50:14,860 --> 00:50:16,260
 I don't know how many times.

838
00:50:16,260 --> 00:50:22,660
 I cannot remember somebody in Hong Kong saying no.

839
00:50:22,660 --> 00:50:30,020
 I actually remember three years ago, I was in Jerusalem,

840
00:50:30,020 --> 00:50:31,900
 I asked somebody if I could pray for him,

841
00:50:31,900 --> 00:50:32,740
 and he actually said no.

842
00:50:32,740 --> 00:50:33,940
 I was taken aback.

843
00:50:33,940 --> 00:50:36,260
 It was the first time that had happened for a while.

844
00:50:36,260 --> 00:50:39,340
 You can pray for people.

845
00:50:39,340 --> 00:50:40,680
 You can minister to them.

846
00:50:40,680 --> 00:50:42,640
 You can show Christ love.

847
00:50:42,640 --> 00:50:45,220
 (gentle music)

848
00:50:45,220 --> 00:50:53,020
 We need the Holy Spirit for the people of Yuen Long.

849
00:50:53,020 --> 00:50:57,200
 It's no point us going to Yuen Long

850
00:50:57,200 --> 00:51:00,060
 with a great plan for a church plant.

851
00:51:00,060 --> 00:51:04,060
 We need the Holy Spirit.

852
00:51:04,060 --> 00:51:10,560
 Let's just wait on Him.

853
00:51:11,760 --> 00:51:13,840
 Allow Him to fill you afresh.

854
00:51:13,840 --> 00:51:19,780
 Worship Him in your hearts.

855
00:51:19,780 --> 00:51:28,220
 Come Holy Spirit.

856
00:51:28,220 --> 00:51:33,240
 (speaking in foreign language)

857
00:51:33,240 --> 00:51:35,820
 (gentle music)

858
00:51:35,820 --> 00:51:38,400
 (gentle music)

